{"tid":1081702,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好耐冇試過食飯食得咁溫暖","createTime":"2019-03-28T12:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T04:32:45.000Z","uid":33143,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"02534a4f4895a969ca9250c9d6f02adb83dae24d","tid":1081702,"uid":33143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"話說呢排有少少感冒<br />\n中午睇完醫生諗住去葵廣食碗牛腩飯之後返工<br />\n之後就有個女仔坐左埋黎我對面<br />\n個女仔幾靚 但作為毒撚既我一直不敢直視所以只能夠一路碌電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知食完個飯發現冇帶tissue 又成口咖哩汁 間餐廳又冇紙巾比<br />\n好彩咁岩見到對面個女仔台上有包tissue<br />\n然後諗諗下同唔識嘅人借tissue又好似好怪<br />\n但係係成口咖哩汁又流緊鼻水咁狼狽嘅情況下唯有唔知醜D問佢借啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢唔單只成包比左我 我拎左一張之後仲好好心問我要唔要多幾張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果下真係好warm 因為果陣鼻水猛咁流 一張真係唔多夠 但又唔好意思話要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準備埋單走果陣佢又對住我微笑 先發覺佢真係笑得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然只係小事 但係如果你係呢位女仔嘅話我好想係到多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望有緣可以再同你坐一台食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114ed77cea539eef4783f16ec82f70957c864d37","tid":1081702,"uid":201604,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:32:44.000Z","msg":"包紙巾畀你掂過仲點要呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1321e6401627bdccebe59db84df4b5f8fe171f62","tid":1081702,"uid":87272,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"見唔見佢急急腳走 知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da6542bd072b148a97fec0c6bc2c69a615b1d7b","tid":1081702,"uid":167186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:36:17.000Z","msg":"成包紙巾都係鼻涕點要呀"},{"pid":"7dfd864841ca8264ebf4eeca23a6a22082f25c86","tid":1081702,"uid":33143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"114ed77cea539eef4783f16ec82f70957c864d37","tid":1081702,"uid":201604,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:32:44.000Z","msg":"包紙巾畀你掂過仲點要呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765a29a1a97bc12aa3d370441f036342628e1c59","tid":1081702,"uid":224952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:44:30.000Z","msg":"唔洗多謝 關懷弱智人士係公民責任"},{"pid":"c7ddb4986c57cfeb54efecafe047d0a79a6afe50","tid":1081702,"uid":33143,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"1321e6401627bdccebe59db84df4b5f8fe171f62","tid":1081702,"uid":87272,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"見唔見佢急急腳走 知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:45:38.000Z","msg":"我走左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係要返工嘅話我應該會坐到佢食完走為止<br />\n好掛住果陣感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94bcf5e2abc0034c7b4592da32ff21f8e58147e","tid":1081702,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:47:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a0b87281f107be3b2d0cddb7c05cbf6c3bb1b9","tid":1081702,"uid":162539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:48:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">仲好好心問我要唔要多幾張</span><br />\n<br />\n可能你個咀以至塊面真係好污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578d268e775414301b60d312c701d3d5ae1247bc","tid":1081702,"uid":40428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:51:38.000Z","msg":"細個一個人食野試過倒瀉杯飲品落地下 <br />\n枱面 條褲又濕哂<br />\n<br />\n隔離枱 有對情侶成包紙巾比哂我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住埋單9秒9走去7仔買番包比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d6b0ac7fadd6261c13a1d34d806f6b163c846f","tid":1081702,"uid":114826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T13:03:18.000Z","msg":"清醒啲啦，佢唔係對住你笑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398341f8fcdc47c3af24db2f6cc55245c9a06707","tid":1081702,"uid":33143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9a0b87281f107be3b2d0cddb7c05cbf6c3bb1b9","tid":1081702,"uid":162539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:48:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">仲好好心問我要唔要多幾張</span><br />\n<br />\n可能你個咀以至塊面真係好污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T13:46:09.000Z","msg":"又咖哩又鼻水我諗都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ba43fe00027649d2b521dc28ca3ac1ccdc4ef1","tid":1081702,"uid":33143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"食飯時間推一推希望佢見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}